his neck like an albatross manley said 
hes no pal of mine but if you look at the thing objectively 
the fact is the 1975 deficit was inherited and somebody had to 
pay it he said did he repeal the surtax no the legislature 
did he went along but i dont think its fair to say in any 
way that hes a tax raiser 
