minister svend robinson were seen traipsing hand in hand through 
the park with his male lover 
is canada ready for this the columnist asked 
robinson said he knows of three other legislators who have 
revealed their homosexuality labor member of parliament chris 
smith in britain and congressmen gerry studds and barney frank 
from massachusetts 
robinson acknowledged political risks but was confident he 
would be renominated for his seat this weekend 
pollster angus reid said the new democrats would find it harder 
to shed their fringeparty image the financial post commented 
the reality is that there is an undercurrent of fear of 
homosexuals in canada 
robinson didnt shed all his apprehensions he asked a reporter 
if his story would reach us newspapers ive got relatives in 
the states and some are aware and some arent he said 
