from his hospital bed he said the gunmen spared his life when he 
obeyed their command to shout kalistan zindabad long live 
kalistan 
kalistan is the name of the nation sikhs envision for themselves 
more than 380 people have been killed by sikh extremists in 
punjab so far this year 
