clore agreement which gave clore the right to nominate a majority 
of the board in exchange for a 140 million investment last year 
they said in the lawsuit that driven by his financial 
desperation and in violation of delaware law and his agreement 
with kaisertech clore has entered into agreements with hurwitz 
under which clore will pretend to nominate his own slate of 
directors but in fact will nominate only those hurwitz selects 
